            <div class="title">
              Rules &#38; Regulations
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Self-drive Rates</div>
              <p>
                The rates are based on a minimum of 24 hours, and should the rental at 
                the time of return, incur excess hours, the charge will be 1/5th of the 
                Contract Rates.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Deliver and Collection Service</div>
              <p>
                Delivery and collection services will be chargeable from RM30 upwards 
                depending on the distance and accessibility of destination from rental location.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Prohibited Odours</div>
              <ol>
                <li>Strictly Do Not Smoke In Our Vehicles.</li> 
                <li>
                  All items and goods discharging unpleasant odors are strictly forbidden 
                  from being carried in the vehicle (e.g. Durians, salted fish etc.). 
                  The renter will be liable to reimburse our car on demand for all costs 
                  of eliminating such odors, including the servicing of the whole air 
                  conditioner system and the loss of rental days to Us.
                </li>
              </ol>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Insurance</div>
              <p>
                The rental rates shown include full indemnity for accidental damage to third 
                party property. However, in line with the commercial insurance practice, the 
                Renter is always responsible for an amount equivalent to the excess clause as 
                follows:
              </p>
              <div class="rules-insurance-table-div">
                <table class="table table-hover rules-insurance-table">
                  <tr>
                    <th>Car Group</th>
                    <th>Excess Clause</th>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td>A</td>
                    <td>RM 1500.00</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td>B</td>
                    <td>RM 2,000.00</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td>C</td>
                    <td>RM 2,500.00</td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </div>
              <p>
                Renter is reminded that underbody, overhead damage is at the Renter's risk at 
                all time and all insurance is void if vehicles are driven on unsealed and 
                unmade roads or surfaces. Missing of vehicle accessories not protected. 
                All rentals are subject to the full terms and conditions set out in the 
                Rental Agreement.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Damages</div>
              <p>
                The renter shall be held responsible for all damages caused to the vehicle, 
                including theft regardless of fault. Upon the renter's acceptance and subject 
                to the terms and conditions stipulated in the Rental Agreement.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Terms of Payment</div>
              <p>
                Only cash payment upon pickup of the vehicle.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Driver's Licence</div>
              <p>
                We recognize Malaysian driving licenses. Overseas tourists may use current 
                issued licenses by their country of residence. 
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Extension of Rental</div>
              <p>
                Any extension of rental beyond the agreed return date and time must be informed 
                in advance with the required additional rental paid.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Rent-It-Here, Leave-It-There</div>
              <p>
                One-way Rental service is available for Renter's convenience. However, 
                a minimum of 4 days rental plus repositioning fee is applicable. Details 
                will be available at the time of enquiry. 
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Restricted Entry</div>
              <p>
                All our cars are strictly prohibited from being driven into Singapore, 
                Thailand and Indonesia.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Parking Charges and Traffic Offence</div>
              <p>
                All traffic, parking offences, courts costs and other expenses that may 
                assessed against us which are due by the reason of Renter's possession or use 
                of our vehicle, will be fully borne by the Renter. We will contact the Renter 
                where possible if it receives parking or traffic summons pertaining to the 
                period under rental. Otherwise, Renter's particulars will be submitted to the 
                authority concerned.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Refund of Unused Services</div>
              <p>
                No refunds, either in part or in full, will be made for unused service and the 
                security deposit (RM300) will be only refund to customers after two weeks of 
                time period so that it will allow us to check amy summons after the vehicle used 
                by the customers.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Navigation System (GPS)</div>
              <p>
                The renter can also add Navigation System (GPS) devices to all car rentals. 
                Daily rental at RM20, monthly rental at RM150 and a flat rate of RM100 for lease 
                rentals. For transient rentals, a maximum of RM200 will be charged. In the event 
                of theft or damage to the GPS device, the renter will be subjected to an excess 
                fee up to a maximum of RM1,000. Purchase of GPS is available upon vehicle collection 
                and it is subject to the availability.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Vehicle Condition</div>
              <p>
                Upon return, the car has to be in the same condition as when it was rented. 
                Failing which, the renter will be liable for the cost of restoring the vehicle 
                to its original condition.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rules-div">
              <div class="container-col-title">Surcharge</div>
              <p>
                A sum of RM50 will be levied for services rendered, after business hours, 
                inclusive of Sundays and Public Holidays. (Business Hour :10am-10pm).
              </p>
